{"tid":1200051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要記住我地既民意基數係100萬人 我地要團結比信心未出黎既人","createTime":"2019-06-10T16:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T16:30:46.000Z","uid":41389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"620448c46036b9a8d63b356d5869fc89f3d3e16c","tid":1200051,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"好多人可能惗緊背後有家庭 有成就 有未來 唔想出黎幫拖<br />\n但我地要用行動真真實實講個事實比佢地聽<br />\n係時間出黎 無分你我 <br />\n黑警面前大家都係戰友 唔會比任何一個拉過去<br />\n肯突破和理非非 我地既人只會越黎越多<br />\n理撚得佢咪啦撚曬入獄囉 定性100萬人暴動囉 <br />\n全香港都錯 唔明白 搬曬入獄就岩<br />\n大家要團結 企出黎 唔好做縮頭烏龜！！！"},{"pid":"8a41b5f0711a8af540cd8f894a4bd42d99fc868d","tid":1200051,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153b9f8dd17a0ab7f7f632cce568886329dbaf04","tid":1200051,"uid":257849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"【大整合】11/6-12/6 資訊整合 「反送中」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199978</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n整合曬資料 唔該大家入黎集中推！"},{"pid":"a1d6f07df00ea43d71a7e99f407e5f844a4bd18c","tid":1200051,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1543b648b23677436310aad822f4bf1128f5da","tid":1200051,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}